  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Euclid's Inferno is a fast-paced 2D shooter where math is your enemy. Play as the father of geometry, explore a hellish version of the works of ancient mathematicians, and defeat polygonal beasts as you upgrade your geometric arsenal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/f08c56fb58e7d3cac81eb3bef9c8c7fa.poster.avif?t=1750996359\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/f08c56fb58e7d3cac81eb3bef9c8c7fa.webm?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/f08c56fb58e7d3cac81eb3bef9c8c7fa.mp4?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Euclid has found himself trapped in a demonic version of his magnum opus <i>The Elements</i> and must traverse the 2D plane and fight against hordes of mathematical constructs.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mathematically Accurate Demons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/8a6d024b167170812fc98096373d1f52.poster.avif?t=1750996359\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/8a6d024b167170812fc98096373d1f52.webm?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/8a6d024b167170812fc98096373d1f52.mp4?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies and bosses inspired in the fundamentals of geometry and the works of past polymaths. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade your Tool set</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/b33ff5c480c8e9c3546f4f4744eaa48c.poster.avif?t=1750996359\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/b33ff5c480c8e9c3546f4f4744eaa48c.webm?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/b33ff5c480c8e9c3546f4f4744eaa48c.mp4?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up new weapons and abilities as you venture deeper into the abstract realms of geometry and arithmetic. Launch points, cast rays and trace circles to defeat your enemies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ad Infinitum</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/835445e98733e3f692f89b7f85c5a8f2.poster.avif?t=1750996359\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/835445e98733e3f692f89b7f85c5a8f2.webm?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/835445e98733e3f692f89b7f85c5a8f2.mp4?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put your skills to the test in the infinite Series, fighting against ever increasing waves of enemies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level Editor</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/e5a53b7eb2fda5459466ddf583249fc5.poster.avif?t=1750996359\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/e5a53b7eb2fda5459466ddf583249fc5.webm?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/e5a53b7eb2fda5459466ddf583249fc5.mp4?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Become the geometer of your own worlds with the custom level editor.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Euclid's Inferno is a fast-paced 2D shooter where math is your enemy. Play as the father of geometry, explore a hellish version of the works of ancient mathematicians, and defeat polygonal beasts as you upgrade your geometric arsenal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/f08c56fb58e7d3cac81eb3bef9c8c7fa.poster.avif?t=1750996359\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/f08c56fb58e7d3cac81eb3bef9c8c7fa.webm?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/f08c56fb58e7d3cac81eb3bef9c8c7fa.mp4?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Euclid has found himself trapped in a demonic version of his magnum opus <i>The Elements</i> and must traverse the 2D plane and fight against hordes of mathematical constructs.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mathematically Accurate Demons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/8a6d024b167170812fc98096373d1f52.poster.avif?t=1750996359\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/8a6d024b167170812fc98096373d1f52.webm?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/8a6d024b167170812fc98096373d1f52.mp4?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies and bosses inspired in the fundamentals of geometry and the works of past polymaths. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade your Tool set</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/b33ff5c480c8e9c3546f4f4744eaa48c.poster.avif?t=1750996359\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/b33ff5c480c8e9c3546f4f4744eaa48c.webm?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/b33ff5c480c8e9c3546f4f4744eaa48c.mp4?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up new weapons and abilities as you venture deeper into the abstract realms of geometry and arithmetic. Launch points, cast rays and trace circles to defeat your enemies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ad Infinitum</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/835445e98733e3f692f89b7f85c5a8f2.poster.avif?t=1750996359\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/835445e98733e3f692f89b7f85c5a8f2.webm?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/835445e98733e3f692f89b7f85c5a8f2.mp4?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put your skills to the test in the infinite Series, fighting against ever increasing waves of enemies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level Editor</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/e5a53b7eb2fda5459466ddf583249fc5.poster.avif?t=1750996359\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/e5a53b7eb2fda5459466ddf583249fc5.webm?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940860/extras/e5a53b7eb2fda5459466ddf583249fc5.mp4?t=1750996359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Become the geometer of your own worlds with the custom level editor.</p>",
